      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/30206dee-b973-11e3-af97-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  3 tests failed: sanity-lfsck, sanityn, sanity.",
