        "subject": "LU-4150 procfs: create nid-stat entry by uuid",
        "message": "LU-4150 procfs: create nid-stat entry by uuid\n\nWe may face wrong deployment while client connection\ncome from same nid. So change nid-stat directory to\nuse client uuid. Add a 'nid' entry in it.\n\nSigned-off-by: yang sheng <yang.sheng@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I0107d5c21fe6be7e5f1a97b5086cd36f6f7bd174\n"
      },
